{"tid":1640626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金澤培譴責有襲擊市民員工被私了　保安資訊被黃絲同事泄漏或威脅安全","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:38:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a0f08708afea755c54c5174bccf1eab5b2f1fca8","tid":1640626,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NorthDistrictTrafficConcernGroupHK/videos/449433612431397/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNorthDistrictTrafficConcernGroupHK%2Fvideos%2F449433612431397%2F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=3794945d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NorthDistrictTrafficConcernGroupHK/videos/449433612431397/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485090-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485090-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=02e5cc5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485090-20191009.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a153419\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485090-20191009.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1485090_1_L_20191009091254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1485090_1_L_20191009091254.jpg&h=e9258a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵行政總裁金澤培向員工發信，形容上星期五經歷了港鐵史上最沉重的一天。多個車站被大肆破壞、蓄意縱火，車務設施大規模受損，列車服務受到極嚴重的影響，由於情況嚴峻，翌日要全綫停駛，形容是艱難的決定，但為了乘客安全，別無他選。對於有前綫員工在執勤時遇襲受傷，金澤培予以譴責，認為施襲者應受到法律制裁。 <br />\n<br />\n金澤培又指出，部分保安資訊被同事泄漏，有可能威脅到其他同事及乘客的安全。他表示，明白員工對公司措施可能持有不同意見，但認為同事和乘客的安全，是不可以妥協。"},{"pid":"5ccba45c0155573621b415a439bf936feabb7881","tid":1640626,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"再裝修囉咁"},{"pid":"27825ac73671cbff545425c889662f683fb1fb07","tid":1640626,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"黨鐵學黑警, 指鹿為馬"},{"pid":"b8848a5aaa377bfbd6a2e75fec85f03b9b038176","tid":1640626,"uid":74155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"黨鐵又吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee3ab91014c9979ba45e65561ac4847af4f8110","tid":1640626,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"歷史必須問因果"},{"pid":"72a600e087750c2a95f7c746abd55d6193d4765a","tid":1640626,"uid":131770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"臥底裝修就屈落示威者"},{"pid":"2eab55d338606106480d12e67751e8af59ce63ca","tid":1640626,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write 